headline: No evidence of gunfire at Naval Medical Center San Diego, military says
content: By Jason Hanna, Greg Botelho, and Michael Martinez, CNNUpdated 0133 GMT (0933 HKT) January 27, 2016  (CNN)A report of a shooting at Naval Medical Center San Diego appears to be a false alarm, the military indicated Tuesday.CNN's Ashley Fantz, Eliott C. McLaughlin, Barbara Starr and Joseph Netto contributed to this report.
